latestPosts.caption:
As I explore brand identities in keywords, the outcome is through a medium of fashion illustrations. It captures two industries - Fashion and Strategy & How they intermingle. 

These illustrations left to right show an illustration that encapsulates @almostgods visual identity, my individualistic take on their identity and an amalgamation of both. 

The idea of this series is to hone my critical analyses and fashion/ visual representation skills. 

• The triangle heads are part of my art style and theres a-lot more to learn and grow from. Feedback is always appreciated 🤞

• Logo use is just for creative purposes; no copyright intended. This is a personal take series on decoding brands and in no way is a byproduct of the brand mentioned above. 

| fashion | visual identity | strategy | illustrations
